_question._questionText: <div><p>Is the statement below true or false:</p><p>&ldquo;The total energy released in fission by a given amount of nuclear fuel is called specific burnup and it is measured in megawatt days [MWd].&rdquo;</p></div><div></div>

<div><p>Is the statement below true or false:</p><p>&ldquo;The fission energy released per unit mass of the fuel is called burnup and it is measured in megawatt days [MWd].&rdquo;</p></div><div></div>
